From 7659f98f3963222de0b1aafa3244c69a8f9b4669 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Zixi Cai <caizx2023@lzu.edu.cn>
Date: Wed, 29 Apr 2026 19:17:45 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] bpf, net: Implement eBPF-based Asynchronous Traffic Shaper
 (ATS) and Time-Aware Shaper (TAS) for TSN

This patch introduces custom modifications to the BPF verifier and adds new kfuncs to support experimental Time-Sensitive Networking (TSN) traffic shaping features directly within the TC/qdisc layer.

Specifically:
1. Inserted bpf_list_node and bpf_rbtree_node into sk_buff and modified the corresponding verifier logic, allowing skb to be added to bpf graph directly.
2. Implemented ATS and TAS shaper in bpf_qdisc.

Signed-off-by: Zixi Cai <caizx2023@lzu.edu.cn>
